 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/09/Oasisticket-prices-Isle-Of-Wight-boss-comments-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/09/Oasisticket-prices-Isle-Of-Wight-boss-comments-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/09/Oasisticket-prices-Isle-Of-Wight-boss-comments-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/09/Oasisticket-prices-Isle-Of-Wight-boss-comments-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/09/Oasisticket-prices-Isle-Of-Wight-boss-comments-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="(max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /></p><p><a href="https://www.nme.com/festivals/isle-of-wight-festival">怀特岛音乐节</a>老板约翰·吉丁斯 (John Giddings) 为<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/oasis">绿洲乐队 (Oasis)</a>辩护，因为他们因<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/oasis-reunion-tour-uk-ireland-stadium-2025-liam-noel-gallagher-tickets-3787539">2025 年重聚巡演的</a>票价而受到强烈反对。</p><p>在庆祝 IOW Fest 历史的展览“Experience 25”上，吉丁斯解释道（通过<a href="https://www.music-news.com/news/UK/176646/Isle-of-Wight-festival-boss-John-Giddings-defends-Oasis-after-reunion-ticket-furore" target="_blank" rel="noopener"><em>音乐新闻</em></a>）：“我认为他们预计会有很大的需求，我不认为他们预计会有超过 1000 万人申请。”超过一百万张门票。</p><ul class="post-content-read-more"><li><strong>阅读更多：</strong> <a href="https://www.nme.com/features/music-features/oasis-reunion-line-up-band-members-guide-3788552"><strong>支持我：2025 年绿洲阵容中的所有球员</strong></a></li></ul><p>“人们没有意识到，也没有意识到的是，在票价中，票价的 20% 在开始之前就以增值税的形式上缴给了政府。”</p><p>他继续说道：“自新<a href="https://www.nme.com/tag/coronavirus">冠疫情</a>、英国<a href="https://www.nme.com/tag/brexit">脱欧</a>以来，举办展览的成本增加了 10 倍，而艺术家们都想举办一场展览。后屏幕、烟花以及随之而来的一切。</p><p> “这就是观众想要的，因为我们可以通过他们购买的门票数量看出。人们用脚投票——如果他们不想来，那我们就都死在水里了。”</p><p>吉丁斯是一名音乐经纪人和推广人，并担任<a href="https://www.solo.uk.com/" target="_blank" rel="noopener">Solo Music Agency</a>的董事总经理。他曾为<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/david-bowie">David Bowie</a>等人工作过，并代理过<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/lady-gaga">Lady Gaga</a> 、 <a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/the-police">The Police</a>和<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/simple-minds">Simple Minds</a>等艺术家。</p><p>尽管怀特岛老板对 Oasis 的票务争议发表了评论，但<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/liam-gallagher">Liam</a>和<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/noel-gallagher">Noel Gallagher</a>不太可能成为 2025 年吉丁斯音乐节的主角。</p><p>八月， <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/oasis-respond-to-glastonbury-2025-rumours-and-the-chances-of-other-festivals-3788269">该英伦流行乐队关闭了有关格拉斯顿伯里音乐节潜在演出机会的报道</a>，并表示他们不会出现在“明年的任何其他音乐节”上。</p><p>对 Oasis 2025 年大型体育场巡演的需求空前高涨，此前关系疏远的加拉格尔兄弟将在巡演中 16 年来首次同台演出。 </p><p><iframe loading="lazy" title="绿洲 - Oasis Live &#39;25 [官方预告片]" width="696" height="392" src="https://www.youtube.com/embed/gol_JnuEtKM?feature=oembed&enablejsapi=1" frameborder="0" allow="accelerometer; autoplay; clipboard-write; encrypted-media; gyroscope; picture-in-picture; web-share" referrerpolicy="strict-origin-when-cross-origin" allowfullscreen></iframe></p><p>随后的一份新闻稿证实，来自 158 个国家的超过 1000 万粉丝试图抢票，这意味着官方票务平台难以应对。</p><p> 8 月 31 日<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/oasis-reunion-2025-fans-frustrated-as-theyre-held-in-long-queues-on-ticketmaster-3789320">门票发售时，数十万粉丝在网上排队等候。</a>许多人被错误识别为兜售门票的机器人后被踢出系统。</p><p>此外， <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/oasis-fans-react-to-ticketmasters-dynamic-pricing-3789361">由于 Ticketmaster 的“动态定价”功能（根据需求自动上涨），人们普遍抱怨价格飙升</a>。粉丝们<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/oasis-reunion-tour-hundreds-complain-to-asa-over-surge-ticket-pricing-3789875">向广告标准局报告了这一情况</a>（ <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/oasis-ticket-sales-culture-secretary-lisa-nandy-calls-for-review-into-dynamic-pricing-and-secondary-ticket-sites-3789694">英国政府</a>和<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/the-european-commission-reportedly-investigating-dynamic-pricing-amid-oasis-tickets-controversy-3790240">欧盟委员会</a>建议进行调查）。</p><p>根据专家的说法， <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/not-warning-oasis-fans-of-dynamic-pricing-may-be-law-breach-experts-say-3789896">在出售之前，不警告粉丝“动态定价”可能是对消费者法的违反</a>。</p><p> <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/oasis-ticket-sales-culture-secretary-lisa-nandy-calls-for-review-into-dynamic-pricing-and-secondary-ticket-sites-3789694">文化部长丽莎·南迪（Lisa Nandy）也进行了权衡，呼吁对政策和次要票务进行审查</a>。 </p><blockquote class="instagram-media" data-instgrm-captioned data-instgrm-permalink="https://www.instagram.com/p/C_V_aXsM96C/?utm_source=ig_embed&amp;utm_campaign=loading" data-instgrm-version="14" style=" background:#FFF; border:0; border-radius:3px; box-shadow:0 0 1px 0 rgba(0,0,0,0.5),0 1px 10px 0 rgba(0,0,0,0.15); margin: 1px; max-width:658px; min-width:326px; padding:0; width:99.375%; width:-webkit-calc(100% - 2px); width:calc(100% - 2px);"><div style="padding:16px;"><div style="background-color: #F4F4F4; border-radius: 50%; flex-grow: 0; height: 40px; margin-right: 14px; width: 40px;"></div><div style="display: flex; flex-direction: column; flex-grow: 1; justify-content: center;"><div style=" background-color: #F4F4F4; border-radius: 4px; flex-grow: 0; height: 14px; margin-bottom: 6px; width: 100px;"></div><div style=" background-color: #F4F4F4; border-radius: 4px; flex-grow: 0; height: 14px; width: 60px;"></div></div></div><div style="padding: 19% 0;"></div><div style="display:block; height:50px; margin:0 auto 12px; width:50px;"><svg width="50px" height="50px" viewBox="0 0 60 60" version="1.1" xmlns="https://www.w3.org/2000/svg" xmlns:xlink="https://www.w3.org/1999/xlink"><g stroke="none" stroke-width="1" fill="none" fill-rule="evenodd"><g transform="translate(-511.000000, -20.000000)" fill="#000000"><g><path d="M556.869,30.41 C554.814,30.41 553.148,32.076 553.148,34.131 C553.148,36.186 554.814,37.852 556.869,37.852 C558.924,37.852 560.59,36.186 560.59,34.131 C560.59,32.076 558.924,30.41 556.869,30.41 M541,60.657 C535.114,60.657 530.342,55.887 530.342,50 C530.342,44.114 535.114,39.342 541,39.342 C546.887,39.342 551.658,44.114 551.658,50 C551.658,55.887 546.887,60.657 541,60.657 M541,33.886 C532.1,33.886 524.886,41.1 524.886,50 C524.8